latestIgtvVideos.title: ✨10 must haves beauty products from @mynykaa✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
@maybelline fit me foundation - light to medium coverage perfect for 
Everyday use.
- Satin finish.
- Lasts up to 5-6 hours.
- Buildable without making it cakey.
- Easy to blend.
@maybelline fit me concealer - Best for everyday use .
- Affordable , easy to blend.
- light-medium coverage and best part its satin finish which gives natural looking skin.
Shade -1 honey 30
Peachy undertone to cover dark circles and pigmentation.

Shade-2 light 10 
For highlighting.

@laneigeindia lip #sleepingmask
Apply before sleeping or nytime of the day for baby soft lips.
@clinique_in moisture surge - Best moisturiser for very dry skin
- instantly hydrates the skin
- Also hydrates very dry area and flackyness
@innisfreeindia jeju volcanic blackhead 3 step program 
My pores get clogged very easily which leads to blackheads very often, i have tried alot of blackhead removing stripes and masks , none of them worked as good as innsfree stripes it deep cleans my pores and blackhead which lasts up to 15 days.
@maccosmeticsindia strobe creme in peach light - Best - Best primer for dry and dull skin.
- Achieve natural and glowing makeup look.
- Must have product in your vanity

@toofaced lip injection - Get fuller and plumped lips in 10 mins.
- Apply before liquid lipstick for smooth application .
- No more cracked line on lips.
@wetnwildindia lipstick in bare it all
- Perfect peachy nude for indian skin tone .
- Creamy formula and pigmented.
- very affordable .
@simpleskincareindia wipes
- Amazing for sensitive skin.
- Doesn’t irritates skin also does not clog pores .
@loccitaneme hand and nails cream
- Best hand cream for very dry and dull skin.
If your hands get very dry and cuts from constant hand wash than this hand cream is for you...i always carry with me while travelling.

I hope you guys like it..❤️🙏🏼❤️
